<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Georg von Leonrod</head><p>Der Rat bittet den N. Mühlkunz von Adelmannsdorf, Armmann des Erhard I. Schürstab, Bürger zu Nürnberg, zu sichern.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_375" id="187r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_375_r1l18">Gorgen von 
<del rend="strikethrough">Loe </del> Leorod </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_375_r1l20"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Görg / vns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> Erhart Schuͤrſtab vnſer <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_375_r1l21">vvie daʒ der Mülkuncʒ von Adelmanſtorff ſein Armman </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_375_r1l22">vor ew vnſıcher ſeẏ / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr Jn ſıchern wöllet auf <expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_375_r1l23">reht / des 
<del rend="strikethrough">ew </del> der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> vnſer <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> von Jm </del> ew oder <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_375_r1l24"><expan>ſcheimbote<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gevvalte von Jm gern helffen vvil </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_375_r1l25">vvenn Er des ermant wirdt / das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc / vnd lat vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_375_r1l26">des ewr <expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wıderwiſſen bey dıſem <expan>bote<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_375" id="187r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Gorgen von Leorod </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Görg, uns hat
                            <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> Erhart Schuͤrstab, unser
                                <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, wie daz der Mülkuncz von
                        Adelmanstorff, sein armman, vor ew unsicher sey.
                            <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir in sichern wöllet auf
                                <expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> reht, des der
                                <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> unser
                            <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> ew oder <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>scheimbote<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalte von im gern helffen wil, wenn er des
                        ermant wirdt. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Und lat uns des ewr
                                <expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider wissen bey disem
                            <expan>bote<ex>n</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
